data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the charming heart of McGregor, Texas! This gorgeous three-bedroom, two-bathroom residence is an absolute gem, spacious living, modern amenities, plus a large fenced backyard.  Wonderful family room with gorgeous wood mantle over electric fireplace, vaulted ceiling, all open to kitchen and dining. Fabulous kitchen with island that has seating and storage, eat at bar, dishwasher, stove, microwave, walk in pantry, and excellent storage thru out.  Great sized bedrooms and closet space. Unwind in the luxurious primary suite that features a walk-in closet, and a well laid bathroom with 2 sinks, soaking tub, and a walk in shower.  Additional features include beautiful fixtures thru out, ring doorbell, Nest, foam insulation, double pane windows, 2 car garage wired for home charging station, double gate on side of home, with additional parking for boat, camper, etc. Rest easy knowing that this home has been professionally appraised by a certified appraiser, September 2023, and is priced below its appraised value $295,000. Priced to sell and move in ready.
